{"tid":1237780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"齊來撚狗 《撐警隊 反暴力》民間聲援大會","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:46:27.000Z","uid":31122,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9efa88db05ee35474371c9d967e7d2bb5db1db74","tid":1237780,"uid":31122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:38:17.000Z","msg":"《撐警隊 反暴力》民間聲援大會<br />\n<br />\n大會主題：<br />\n凝聚警隊支持者，為警隊打氣，民意授權警隊有效執法<br />\n<br />\n日期：6月30日 星期日<br />\n時間：下午3-6點<br />\n地點：金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n近日警隊執法受到政治惡勢力無理指責，驅散暴徒被抹黑成過度武力，嚴重影響警隊士氣和市民對警隊執法信心；我們堅信香港警隊是優秀專業紀律部隊，信任警隊能有效依法執行職務，除暴安良維持社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n香港政研會聯合立法會新界西議員何君堯律師為警隊打打氣，誠邀您一起集氣，驅走社會上的瘴氣歪風；香港警察守護我們的治安，今天讓我們來守護警隊的尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n撐警隊、反暴力！<br />\n支持香港警隊有效執法！<br />\n<br />\n約定您：<br />\n金鐘添馬公園<br />\n6月30日 週日<br />\n下午3至6時<br />\n<br />\n別讓惡勢力歪風破壞法治，一起走出來說正言。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎不同團體及市民出席，是次活動為民間自發活動，香港政研會只為籌辦及執行單位，大會主辦及參與者皆為市民個人，不分彼此。<br />\n<br />\n本活動不接受任何捐款捐獻，也不會安排任何物資派發，我們只需要您的氣場，為香港未來打氣。<br />\n<br />\n#撐警隊反暴力<br />\n#支持香港警察<br />\n#有效執法<br />\n#何君堯<br />\n#香港政研會<br />\n<br />\n傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/214071328963264/posts/851776835192707?s=1383949581&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F214071328963264%2Fposts%2F851776835192707%3Fs%3D1383949581%26sfns%3Dmo&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=3f8f70c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/214071328963264/posts/851776835192707?s=1383949581&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"11726b2697cc38a0891fd1cf52f3a550286c92bb","tid":1237780,"uid":31122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AWOeWPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAWOeWPg.png&h=10acfc76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ee62157ba0492cb6f8d1e964ee34ec288691b00","tid":1237780,"uid":208296,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gw3ZouG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGw3ZouG.png&h=8bf6e8ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c63f065627b6563be629dc863c800b6d00101943","tid":1237780,"uid":649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"去左一陣比人count人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0085f849286267708b6d5cd11ce7816c591129","tid":1237780,"uid":31122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c63f065627b6563be629dc863c800b6d00101943","tid":1237780,"uid":649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"去左一陣比人count人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"放心 佢地有毅進制 逢1進100<br />\n好快突破300萬大關"}]}